Veda system project.

I. Project dependencies
	1. OTP/Erlang R15
	2. Mochiweb (pulled automatically by rebar)
	3. Webmachine (pulled automatically by rebar)
	4. ErlyDTL (pulled automatically by rebar)
	5. HAProxy

II. Building & running:
0. Build the veda system:
   $ make

1. Start up the veda@client & veda@core applications:
   $ make start

2. Start up the haproxy application for load balancing:
   $ make proxystart
